text: Katri Kalpala (born September 29, 1976 in Helsinki) is a Finnish rhythmic gymnast. Kalpala competed for Finland in the rhythmic gymnastics individual all-around competition at the 1996 Summer Olympics in Atlanta. There she was 34th in the qualification round and did not advance to the semifinal. == Family == Her father is businessman Asmo Kalpala (fi). == References == == External links == * * Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish rhythmic gymnasts Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic gymnasts of Finland Category:Sportspeople from Helsinki
